[The text of the following West Nile Virus Surveillance Information
(arranged by Health Region) is supplemented by comprehensive maps
which can be viewed by accessing the Health Canada web-site using the
URLs given below. Also the abbreviated tables compiled below have
been simplified by merging the probable and confirmed columns, and
deleting the footnotes describing the case definitions and other
specific matters. - Mod.CP]
